TabBar

Ancestors Scrollable > StatefulComponent > Widget

Displays a horizontal row of tabs, one per label. If isScrollable is true then each tab is as wide as needed for its label and the entire [TabBar] is scrollable. Otherwise each tab gets an equal share of the available space. A [TabBarSelection] widget ancestor must have been built to enable saving and monitoring the selected tab.

  child: new Chip(
    label: new Text('Lorem Ipsum')
